data.description: Come Check out this 3 bedroom 1 and a half bath house in the much desired Unit 7 School District. Inside you will find a large eat in  kitchen with plenty of storage. There is also a large bonus room that could be used for entertaining or even as an extra bedroom. The fenced in back yard has deck for entertaining and a 2 car detached garage with alley access. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this your own! Recent updates include furnace, water heater, and updated 200 amp electrical system.
